&+WPolicies
&+b--------
Type POLICY [policy] to read a policy:

  * ads       : What we think of advertising for other MUDs on this MUD.
  * harass    : Harassment will not be tolerated.
  * clone     : Cloning &+W(Wizards, READ THIS)&*
  * cheat     : What is considered cheating (Wizards and mortals)
  * lagdeath  : Our policy on the deadly LagMonster.
  * cut       : Cutting connections
  * frob      : The frobbing policy
  * healing   : The healing policy
